These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, carrot, garlic
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, red, ebony, turquise
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, epic, family, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, dubstep, electronic
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, horse, mouse
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
 2. the person who likes red is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 5. the fan of classical is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the fan of d&b is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 9. the person watching family movies is the person eating asparagus##1
10. the owner of the horse is the person watching epic movies##1
11. the person who likes amber is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | cabbage    | carrot      | asparagus  | garlic     |
| Color         | turquise    | ebony   | amber | red      |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | documentary | family     | romance    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | d&b         | classical  | dubstep    |
| Pet           | horse      | mouse       | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

