The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, romance, family, satire
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, taxi, trike
 1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the thai is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the japanese##1
 9. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | sprite   | cola      | coffee     |
| Food          | pepper     | garlic   | raspberry | grapefruit |
| Nationality   | indonesian | japanese | chinese   | thai       |
| Movie-Genre           | romance       | martial-arts      | satire     | family |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | taxi     | trike     | roller     |

