 3. the canadian is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the person who likes azure##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
 6. the musician is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the dancer##1
 9. the person who likes lilac is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the australian is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the journalist is on the far left##1
13. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
14. the spanish is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
